(67, 1, '2018-05-24 13:04:43', '2018-05-24 13:04:43', '<h1>Pastor Michael Lynn Miller, Sr.</h1>\r\n<h3>Lead Pastor</h3>\r\n<strong>Lead Pastor Michael Lynn Miller</strong> has served in full time ministry for 18 years. He recently served as Assistant to Dr. Pat Robertson, Chairman of Christian Broadcasting Network (CBN, 700 Club, Operation Blessing). He also is founding Pastor of Triumphant Life Church in Asbury Park NJ, where he served for 12 years. Pastor Miller graduated from Evangelical Bible Institute and attended Global University. He has served on various executive boards. He also served as a Development Officer for Star 99.1 FM radio and Solutions Pregnancy Center. Pastor Miller is best known for his prophetic pastoral ministry. His passion for mentoring in the local church has produced many sons and daughters in the ministry. His ministry has taken him to serve international ministry leaders, as well as, business leaders. Pastor Miller is a lifelong resident of New Jersey. He is a loving father to his children, which is his first ministry.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>Pastor Linda Parreott</h1>\r\n<h3>Executive Pastor</h3>\r\n<strong>Pastor Linda Parreott</strong> was born in Killeen, Texas to Dr. &amp; Rev. John C Smith and Evangelist Juanita Hannah. She was ordained to the Pastorate in 1994. She is currently employed full time by New Jersey Natural Gas Company as a supervisor. Having taken several online Bible courses and receiving certificates from local Bible Institutes, Reverend Linda is currently pursuing bachelor’s degree in Business Management.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1>Elder Andrew Sawyer</h1>\r\n<h3>Elder</h3>\r\n<strong>Elder Andrew Sawyer </strong>migrated to the United States with his family from Freetown Sierra Leone in 1995.\r\n<div>He loves the Lord and is passionate about the things of God. He served as Prayer Leader for four years, Executive Board Member for 6 years, Leader for Nursing Home ministry for over 10 years and is currently serving as a Deacon, an office he has held for over 15 years. He is married to Minister Regina Sawyer, a union that has spanned for over 28 years. They are blessed with three beautiful children, Andrena, Ethleen and Hannah.</div>', 'Leadership Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-24 13:04:43', '2018-05-24 13:04:43', '', 26, 'http://localhost/higherpurpose/2018/05/24/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
