(137, 1, '2018-05-28 20:39:56', '2018-05-28 20:39:56', '<div id=\"helping-hands\" class=\"ministry\">\nHelping Hands Project\nThis will be the community development corporation for HPF. This is an outreach from HPF to the greater community. Three areas of focus will be to engage single and disadvantaged mothers, domestic violence and drug abuse. We also provide services to the community through adopt-a-block and our annual Christmas toy drive.\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"inner-healing\" class=\"ministry\">\nInner Healing\nMore details to come.\n</div>\n\n \n<div id=\"mens-ministry\" class=\"ministry\">\nMen of Purpose – Men’s Ministry\nThis ministry is designed to provide men with a clear biblical perspective of their role in the home, in the church and in society. This is accomplished through monthly meetings and annual retreats.\n</div>\n \n<div id=\"prae\" class=\"ministry\">\nPrayer & Intercession\nThis ministry is to motivate and provide a prayer focus for the entire church. We will also help build and strengthen the believer’s prayer life. Men are to always pray and not faint.\n</div>\n \n\nReaching the World\nThis ministry provides opportunities to partner with our brothers and sisters around the world. We will take missions trips and underwrite the work of God overseas by sponsorship of water wells.\n\n \n\nSisters & Friends – Women’s Ministry\nEvery woman needs a sister and a friend. This ministry is designed to create bonds between women that foster lifelong relationships. This is accomplished by conviviality and relational teaching.', 'Our Ministries', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '18-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-05-28 20:39:56', '2018-05-28 20:39:56', '', 18, 'http://localhost/higherpurpose/2018/05/28/18-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
