(160, 1, '2018-06-02 13:36:40', '2018-06-02 13:36:40', '<div class=\"inner-healing-details\" style=\"float: left;\">\n\nInner healing is the ministry of Jesus- healing the broken-hearted and setting the captives free. Our joy is serving Him and sharing His healing love with the suffering in this broken world.Inner Healing supports the Higher Purpose Fellowship mission of leading people into a God-fulfilled life by helping God’s people get healed and delivered so that they can be all that God has called them to be.\n\nInner healing ministry is made up of a group of trained prayer ministers and is designed to produce breakthrough in the life of the believer.  If your dealing with hurts, challenges, or barriers in your walk with Christ, we would like you to prayerfully consider coming in for a confidential session.\n\nTo schedule a session, <a href=\"http://localhost/higherpurpose/inner-healing-application/\">please fill out the application here</a>.  *UPDATE TO LIVE LINK ONCE LIVE*\n\n</div>\n<img class=\" wp-image-259 alignright\" src=\"http://localhost/higherpurpose/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/deliverance-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"271\" height=\"271\" />', 'Inner Healing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '28-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-06-02 13:36:40', '2018-06-02 13:36:40', '', 28, 'http://localhost/higherpurpose/2018/05/28/28-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
