(192, 1, '2018-06-01 14:58:29', '2018-06-01 14:58:29', 'We\'re excited to announce the beginning of our Summer Camp. Summer Camp will run from July 9th to August 24th, 2018.\r\n\r\nHere are some fun details about camp this year:\r\n<ul style=\"font-family: \'PT Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: #676767;\">\r\n 	<li>Art projects</li>\r\n 	<li>Science &amp; Technology</li>\r\n 	<li>Handwriting Skills</li>\r\n 	<li>Crafts</li>\r\n 	<li>Ice Cream</li>\r\n 	<li>Music</li>\r\n 	<li>And much, much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/higherpurpose/summer-camp-registration-form/\" style=\"color: #1d3f7c; font-weight: bold;\">Click here to register your child/children for Summer Camp. </a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Please Note:</strong> Program Initial registration fee is $25.00. All payments must be received prior to attending the program. No exceptions. Cost per child $98.00 per week for HPF members, $129.00 per week for non-members. A 10% discount will be offered for full participation through the duration of the program for each child enrolled. To make payment(s), please follow the link at the end of this registration form.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, you may contact Jennifer Farley at <a href=\"mailto:summercamphpf@gmail.com\">summercamphpf@gmail.com</a>.', 'HPF Summer Camp 2018', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'hpf-summer-camp-2018', '', '', '2018-06-02 12:33:51', '2018-06-02 12:33:51', '', 0, 'http://localhost/higherpurpose/?page_id=192', 0, 'page', '', 0),
