(204, 1, '2018-06-01 16:57:48', '2018-06-01 16:57:48', '<h2><img class=\"wp-image-81 alignleft\" src=\"http://localhost/higherpurpose/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/pastor-mike-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />Pastor Michael Lynn Miller, Sr.</h2>\r\n<h3>Lead Pastor</h3>\r\n<strong>Lead Pastor Michael Lynn Miller</strong> has served in full time ministry for almost 20 years. He recently served as Assistant to Dr. Pat Robertson, Chairman of Christian Broadcasting Network (CBN, 700 Club, Operation Blessing). He also is founding Pastor of Triumphant Life Church in Asbury Park NJ, where he served for 12 years. Pastor Miller graduated from Evangelical Bible Institute and attended Global University. He has served on various executive boards. He also served as a Development Officer for Star 99.1 FM radio. Pastor Michael is best known for his prophetic pastoral ministry. His passion for mentoring in the local church has produced many sons and daughters in the ministry. His ministry has taken him to serve international ministry leaders, as well as, business leaders. Pastor Miller is a lifelong resident of New Jersey. He is a loving father to his children and grandchildren which are his first ministry.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img class=\" wp-image-83 alignleft\" src=\"http://localhost/higherpurpose/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Pastor-Linda-Parreott-Higher-Purpose-2-1-300x293.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"293\" />Pastor Linda Parreott</h2>\r\n<h2>Executive Pastor</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h2><img class=\"wp-image-82 alignleft\" src=\"http://localhost/higherpurpose/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Sawyer-720x1024-e1527211340363-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />Elder Andrew Sawyer</h2>\r\n<h3>Elder</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-173 alignleft\" src=\"http://localhost/higherpurpose/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/minister-regina-cropped-30